15
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:47,350
And yet many people,
when they come

16
00:00:47,350 --> 00:00:49,510
to the idea of writing
R package, they think,

17
00:00:49,510 --> 00:00:51,130
this is too advanced for me.

18
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:52,570
This is beyond my scope.

19
